  "content": "### Step 5: Run all tests\n### Step 6: Commit\n\n## Post-Implementation Checklist\n\nAfter all tasks are complete, verify:\n\n- `cargo build --workspace` compiles without errors\n- `cargo test -p corvia-common -- --test-threads=1` — all config tests pass\n- `cargo test -p corvia-kernel -- --test-threads=1` — all kernel tests pass (OllamaEngine, knowledge_files, LiteStore, factory)\n- `cargo test --test e2e_test test_lite_store -- --nocapture` — LiteStore E2E passes\n- `corvia init` creates LiteStore config and `.corvia/` directory\n- `corvia init --full` creates SurrealDB config and provisions Docker (requires Docker)\n- `corvia rebuild` rebuilds LiteStore from knowledge JSON files\n- `corvia status` shows store type and entry count\n- With Ollama running: `corvia ingest .` embeds and stores Corvia's own code\n- With Ollama running: `corvia search \"how does embedding work\"` returns relevant results\n",
